    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows signs of its age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some paint fading on the hood and roof, though there is no major body damage. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and a few small tears in the driver's seat, and the dashboard has some minor cracking. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and suspension work in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional vehicle for someone looking for a dependable driver who doesn't mind some cosmetic and minor mechanical needs.",
      "price": 22500.0,
