      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently requires major mechanical repairs to be drivable, and the exterior has significant rust and body damage. The interior shows heavy wear, including several tears in the upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project for a dedicated mechanic or a valuable source of parts.",
