    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in immaculate, showroom-ready condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is truly uncompromising. This is an exemplary specimen for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection in both aesthetic appeal and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
